snippet.title: Dance of Decapods - Trailer
snippet.description:
A minimalist single screen bullet hell where your space insect must survive waves of enemies. Evolve to fight back with more than 30 different parts, from bio weapons to bullet enhancement.

Available on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1934270/Dance_of_Decapods/
